author: Marcus Cho
title: Fear of God Teams Up With KITH to Release Limited Capsule Collection
text:
Visit the original post to see all 6 images from this gallery. 
Brand: Fear of God x KITH
Season: Spring/Summer 2017
Key Pieces: A set of jacket and pants constructed with premium Japanese nylon with Riri zipper hardware.
Editor’s Notes: This wouldn’t be the first time Fear of God has teamed with another big-name label, and we certainly hope it won’t be the last. The particular color of navy used in this collection also gives the range an extremely wearable vibe; simple from a distance, but luxuriously detailed up-close. The capsule is set to release March 8 at Kith’s Maxfield shop.
Find Out More Be sure to also check out Fear of God’s previous collaboration with Vans.
